data.description: Discover the epitome of modern living in the prestigious Gated Community of Anderson Creek Club. This exquisite 4-bedroom, two and a half bath home boasts a spacious open floorplan designed to meet your every need. On the first floor, you'll find a welcoming family room, a formal dining area, a well-appointed kitchen, convenient laundry room, and a half bathroom. The second floor features the primary bedroom with an en-suite bathroom, complete with a shower and a separate soaking tub. Additionally, two more bedrooms, an oversized bedroom that can double as a bonus room, and an additional bath with dual sinks. Step outside, and you'll be greeted by a screened-in porch and a fenced backyard, perfect for relaxing and entertaining. This home has a remarkable landscape package with stamped concrete galore. POA dues include community amenities, highspeed internet, pools, fitness centers, lawn care, and much more! Seller is offering a $1,000 paint​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ allowance.
